@startuml VibeTags Build Sequence
title VibeTags - Build-Time Processing Sequence

actor Developer
participant "Build Tool\n(Maven/Gradle)" as Build
participant "javac Compiler" as Javac
participant "AIGuardrailProcessor" as Processor
participant "RoundEnvironment" as RoundEnv
participant "File System" as FS
database "AI Config Files" as Output

== Compilation Phase ==

Developer -> Build: mvn clean compile
Build -> Build: Resolve vibetags-processor dependency
Build -> Javac: Invoke Java compiler
Javac -> Javac: Scan source files for annotations

note over Javac
    Discovers processor via SPI:
    META-INF/services/javax.annotation.processing.Processor
    -> com.vibetags.processor.AIGuardrailProcessor
end note

== Annotation Processing Round ==

Javac -> Processor: process(annotations, roundEnv)
activate Processor

Processor -> Processor: Check if annotations empty
alt annotations.isEmpty()
    Processor --> Javac: return false (no processing)
else annotations present
    Processor -> Processor: Determine output path\nPaths.get("").toAbsolutePath()
    
    == Pass 1: Process @AILocked ==
    Processor -> RoundEnv: getElementsAnnotatedWith(AILocked)
    RoundEnv --> Processor: List of @AILocked elements
    
    loop For each @AILocked element
        Processor -> Processor: Extract className + reason
        Processor -> Processor: Append to cursorRules builder
        Processor -> Processor: Append to claudeMd builder
        Processor -> Processor: Append to aiExclude builder
        Processor -> Processor: Append to chatGpt builder
    end
    
    == Pass 2: Process @AIContext ==
    Processor -> RoundEnv: getElementsAnnotatedWith(AIContext)
    RoundEnv --> Processor: List of @AIContext elements
    
    loop For each @AIContext element
        Processor -> Processor: Extract className + focus + avoids
        Processor -> Processor: Append to cursorRules builder
        Processor -> Processor: Append to claudeMd builder
        Processor -> Processor: Append to chatGpt builder
    end
    
    == Pass 3: Process @AIAudit ==
    Processor -> RoundEnv: getElementsAnnotatedWith(AIAudit)
    RoundEnv --> Processor: List of @AIAudit elements
    
    loop For each @AIAudit element
        Processor -> Processor: Extract className + checkFor[]
        
        alt checkFor is empty
            Processor -> Processor: Skip this element
        else checkFor has values
            Processor -> Processor: Append to cursorAudit builder
            Processor -> Processor: Append to claudeAudit builder
            Processor -> Processor: Append to geminiMd builder
            Processor -> Processor: Append to chatGptAudit builder
        end
    end
    
    == Finalize Output ==
    Processor -> Processor: Merge audit sections\nif hasAuditAnnotations
    
    Processor -> FS: Write .cursorrules
    FS --> Processor: File written
    
    Processor -> FS: Write CLAUDE.md
    FS --> Processor: File written
    
    Processor -> FS: Write .aiexclude
    FS --> Processor: File written
    
    Processor -> FS: Write chatgpt_instructions.md
    FS --> Processor: File written
    
    Processor -> FS: Write gemini_instructions.md
    FS --> Processor: File written
    
    Processor --> Javac: return true (annotations claimed)
end

deactivate Processor

== Compilation Complete ==

Javac --> Build: Compilation successful
Build --> Developer: Build complete

note over Output
    Generated Files:
    - .cursorrules (Cursor)
    - CLAUDE.md (Claude)
    - .aiexclude (Gemini)
    - chatgpt_instructions.md (ChatGPT)
    - gemini_instructions.md (Gemini)
end note

== AI Tool Usage (Runtime) ==

note over Developer, Output
    Developer uses AI assistant to modify code
end note

Developer -> Cursor: Request code modification
Cursor -> Cursor: Read .cursorrules
Cursor -> Cursor: Check LOCKED FILES
Cursor -> Cursor: Check MANDATORY SECURITY AUDITS
Cursor --> Developer: AI response (follows guardrails)

@enduml
